import React, { Component } from 'react';
import {Icon, Menu, Sidebar } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';

class AppSidebar extends Component {
    state = { activeItem: 'authorization' }
    handleItemClick = (e, { name }) => this.setState({ activeItem: name })
  
    render() {
      const { activeItem } = this.state
  
      return (
          
        <Sidebar.Pusher>    
            <Sidebar
                as={Menu}
                animation='push'
                direction='left'
                icon='labeled'
                visible='true'
                vertical
                width='thin'
            >
            {/* 1 */}
            <Menu.Item name='authorization' 
                       active={activeItem === 'authorization'} 
                       onClick={this.handleItemClick}>
                <Icon name='user' />
                Authorizations
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 2 */}
            <Menu.Item name='account' 
                        active={activeItem === 'account'} 
                        onClick={this.handleItemClick}>
                <Icon name='user' />
                Accounts
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 3 */}
            <Menu.Item name='plan' 
                        active={activeItem === 'plan'} 
                        onClick={this.handleItemClick}>
                <Icon name='box' />
                Plans
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 4 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='user' />
                Coverage
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 5 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Benefits
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 6 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Procedures
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 7 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Diseases
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 8 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Pharmacies
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 9 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Clusters
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 10 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Exclusions
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 11 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Packages
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 12 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Case Rates
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 13 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                ACU Schedules
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 14 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Facilities
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 15 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Rooms
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 16 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Practitioner
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 17 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Facility Groups
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 18 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Miscellaneous
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 19 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Users
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 20 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Members
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 21 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Roles
            </Menu.Item>
            {/* 22 */}
            <Menu.Item as='a'>
                <Icon name='home' />
                Companies
            </Menu.Item>
            </Sidebar>
            

            </Sidebar.Pusher>
      )
    }
}

export default AppSidebar;
